paragraphs.text:
%sql

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS SALES.COUNTRYUSERS;
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS SALES.REGIONALUSERS;
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS SALES.ALLUSERS;

CREATE TABLE SALES.COUNTRYUSERS
(
Region varchar(50),
Country varchar(50),
ItemType varchar(50),
SalesChannel varchar(50),
OrderPriority varchar(50),
OrderDate date,
OrderID integer,
ShipDate date,
UnitsSold double,
UnitPrice double,
UnitCost double,
TotalRevenue double,
TotalCost double,
TotalProfit double,
UserID varchar(50),
Username varchar(50),
FirstName varchar(50),
LastName varchar(50),
IsRegionManager varchar(50)
)
USING COLUMN OPTIONS (PARTITION_BY 'REGION', BUCKETS '7');

INSERT INTO SALES.COUNTRYUSERS (SELECT R.*, U.USERID, U.USERNAME, U.FIRST_NAME, U.LAST_NAME, U.ISREGIONMANAGER FROM SALES.RECORDS R
 JOIN SALES.USERS U ON R.REGION = U.REGION AND R.COUNTRY = U.COUNTRY WHERE U.ISREGIONMANAGER = 'FALSE');
 
CREATE TABLE SALES.REGIONALUSERS
(
Region varchar(50),
Country varchar(50),
ItemType varchar(50),
SalesChannel varchar(50),
OrderPriority varchar(50),
OrderDate date,
OrderID integer,
ShipDate date,
UnitsSold double,
UnitPrice double,
UnitCost double,
TotalRevenue double,
TotalCost double,
TotalProfit double,
UserID varchar(50),
Username varchar(50),
FirstName varchar(50),
LastName varchar(50),
IsRegionManager varchar(50)
)
USING COLUMN OPTIONS (PARTITION_BY 'REGION', BUCKETS '7');

INSERT INTO SALES.REGIONALUSERS (SELECT R.*, U.USERID, U.USERNAME, U.FIRST_NAME, U.LAST_NAME, U.ISREGIONMANAGER FROM SALES.RECORDS R
 JOIN SALES.USERS U ON R.REGION = U.REGION WHERE U.ISREGIONMANAGER = 'TRUE');
 
 
CREATE TABLE SALES.ALLUSERS USING COLUMN OPTIONS (PARTITION_BY 'REGION', BUCKETS '7') AS
(SELECT * FROM SALES.COUNTRYUSERS);

INSERT INTO SALES.ALLUSERS (SELECT * FROM SALES.REGIONALUSERS);

paragraphs.title: Create Sample Tables
paragraphs.text:
%sql

CREATE SAMPLE TABLE SALES.ALLUSERS_SAMPLE10 ON SALES.ALLUSERS OPTIONS(
    buckets '7', qcs 'country',
    fraction '0.1', 
    strataReservoirSize '50', persistent 'sync') 
  AS (SELECT * FROM SALES.ALLUSERS);

CREATE SAMPLE TABLE SALES.RECORDS_SAMPLE10 ON SALES.RECORDS OPTIONS(
    buckets '7', qcs 'country',
    fraction '0.1', 
    strataReservoirSize '50', persistent 'sync') 
  AS (SELECT * FROM SALES.RECORDS);
